<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_149_r1l14"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> als Jr vns aber <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> yoſep <expan>Jud<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu Dyet = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_149_r1l15">furt <expan>geſeſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gompr<ex>echt</ex></expan> <expan>Jud<ex>en</ex></expan> bey vns wonhaft etc / das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_149_r1l16"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> . Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır eẅch nehſt <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> / daʒ der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>gompr<ex>echt</ex></expan> Jud </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_149_r1l17">dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Joſep <expan>Jud<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>freẅntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> g </del> <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſein wölt vor des Reichs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_149_r1l20"><expan>Rıcht<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_149_line_1577035082771_3039">oder vor der Jüdıſcheıt </ab></add> bey vns ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> / Des auch wır <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> Joſep <expan>Jud<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>fürderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_149_r1l21">helffen <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıchen</expan> in der maſſ als vns dıe <expan>Jüdıſch<ex>eit</ex></expan> bey vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_149_r1l22">
<add>wonhaft</add> von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem <expan>Römıſche<ex>n</ex></expan> etc künıg befolhen ıſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_149_r1l23">Wıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſo <expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan> wır doch vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mıt <expan>gompr<ex>echt</ex></expan> <expan>Jude<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ſou<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_149_line_1577035102864_3055">geredt 
<add><ab facs="#facs_149_line_1577035184208_3120">wıe wol wır des ʒu </ab><ab facs="#facs_149_line_1577035187068_3125">tun nıht ſchuldıg <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> </ab></add> Daʒ er <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> ſein <expan>voll<ex>er</ex></expan> gewalt / der ſache gen dem <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> Joſep </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_149_r1l26"><expan>Jud<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu awſʒtrag <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> wolt vor des <expan>Jude<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Hohmeıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> einem . ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_149_r1l27"><expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> oder ʒu Eger / Vnd ıſt vns nıht füklıch den <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> <expan>gompr<ex>echt</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_149_r1l28"><expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>verr<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu weıſen / Denn wo wır eẅch lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_149_line_1577035125753_3071"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> marie magdalene </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_149" id="73v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Gareysen, <expan>pfleg<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        zu Dyetfürt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, als ir uns aber
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> Yosep <expan>jud<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                        Dyetfurt <expan>gesess<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>Gompr<ex>echt</ex></expan>
<expan>jud<ex>en</ex></expan> bey uns wonhaft etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>.
                        Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ewch nehst
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>, daz der
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>Gompr<ex>echt</ex></expan> jud dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
                        Josep <expan>jud<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sein wölt, vor des reichs
                                <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add>oder vor der jüdischeit</add> bey uns zu
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, des auch wir
                                <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan> Josep
                            <expan>jud<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>fürderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> helffen <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lichen</expan> in der mass, als uns die
                                <expan>jüdisch<ex>eit</ex></expan> bey uns <add>wonhaft</add> von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> dem <expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.
                        künig befolhen ist. Wie <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> so
                                <expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan> wir doch umb
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>Gompr<ex>echt</ex></expan>
<expan>jude<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>sov<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> geredt, <add>wie wol wir des zu tun niht
                            schuldig <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan></add>, daz er
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> sein <expan>voll<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        gewalt der sache gen dem <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> Josep
                                <expan>jud<ex>en</ex></expan> zu awsztrag
                            <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> wolt vor des <expan>jude<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hohmeist<ex>er</ex></expan>, einem zu <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
                        oder zu Eger; und ist uns niht füklich, den
                            <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Gompr<ex>echt</ex></expan>
<expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>verr<ex>er</ex></expan> zu weisen. Denn wo wir ewch lieb
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Marie Magdalene.</ab>
</div>
